priceSpecification.comment: One or more detailed price specifications, indicating the unit price and delivery or payment charges.
priceSpecification.comment_plain: One or more detailed price specifications, indicating the unit price and delivery or payment charges.

priceValidUntil.comment: The date after which the price is no longer available.
priceValidUntil.comment_plain: The date after which the price is no longer available.

printColumn.comment: The number of the column in which the NewsArticle appears in the print edition.
printColumn.comment_plain: The number of the column in which the NewsArticle appears in the print edition.

printEdition.comment: The edition of the print product in which the NewsArticle appears.
printEdition.comment_plain: The edition of the print product in which the NewsArticle appears.

printPage.comment: If this NewsArticle appears in print, this field indicates the name of the page on which the article is found. Please note that this field is intended for the exact page name (e.g. A5, B18).
printPage.comment_plain: If this NewsArticle appears in print, this field indicates the name of the page on which the article is found. Please note that this field is intended for the exact page name (e.g. A5, B18).
printPage.label: Print Page

printSection.comment: If this NewsArticle appears in print, this field indicates the print section in which the article appeared.
printSection.comment_plain: If this NewsArticle appears in print, this field indicates the print section in which the article appeared.
printSection.label: Print Section

productionCompany.comment: The production company or studio that made the movie, TV series, season, or episode, or video.
productionCompany.comment_plain: The production company or studio that made the movie, TV series, season, or episode, or video.
productionCompany.label: Production Company

ratingCount.comment: The count of total number of ratings.
ratingCount.comment_plain: The count of total number of ratings.
ratingCount.label: Rating Count

replyToUrl.comment: The URL at which a reply may be posted to the specified UserComment.
replyToUrl.comment_plain: The URL at which a reply may be posted to the specified UserComment.
replyToUrl.label: Reply to Url

reviewBody.comment: The actual body of the review
reviewBody.comment_plain: The actual body of the review

reviewCount.comment: The count of total number of reviews.
reviewCount.comment_plain: The count of total number of reviews.

reviewRating.comment: The rating given in this review. Note that reviews can themselves be rated. The reviewRating applies to rating given by the review. The aggregateRating property applies to the review itself, as a creative work.
reviewRating.comment_plain: The rating given in this review. Note that reviews can themselves be rated. The reviewRating applies to rating given by the review. The aggregateRating property applies to the review itself, as a creative work.
reviewRating.label: Review Rating

serialNumber.comment: The serial number or any alphanumeric identifier of a particular product. When attached to an offer, it is a shortcut for the serial number of the product included in the offer.
serialNumber.comment_plain: The serial number or any alphanumeric identifier of a particular product. When attached to an offer, it is a shortcut for the serial number of the product included in the offer.
serialNumber.label: Serial Number

sku.comment: The Stock Keeping Unit (SKU), i.e. a merchant-specific identifier for a product or service, or the product to which the offer refers.
sku.comment_plain: The Stock Keeping Unit (SKU), i.e. a merchant-specific identifier for a product or service, or the product to which the offer refers.
sku.label: Sku

startDate.comment: The start date and time of the event (in ISO 8601 date format).
startDate.comment_plain: The start date and time of the event (in ISO 8601 date format).

subEvent.comment: An Event that is part of this event. For example, a conference event includes many presentations, each are a subEvent of the conference.
subEvent.comment_plain: An Event that is part of this event. For example, a conference event includes many presentations, each are a subEvent of the conference.
subEvent.label: Sub Event

subEvents.comment: Events that are a part of this event. For example, a conference event includes many presentations, each are subEvents of the conference (legacy spelling; see singular form, subEvent).
subEvents.comment_plain: Events that are a part of this event. For example, a conference event includes many presentations, each are subEvents of the conference (legacy spelling; see singular form, subEvent).
subEvents.label: Sub Events

superEvent.comment: An event that this event is a part of. For example, a collection of individual music performances might each have a music festival as their superEvent.
superEvent.comment_plain: An event that this event is a part of. For example, a collection of individual music performances might each have a music festival as their superEvent.
superEvent.label: Super Event

transcript.comment: If this MediaObject is an AudioObject or VideoObject, the transcript of that object.
transcript.comment_plain: If this MediaObject is an AudioObject or VideoObject, the transcript of that object.
transcript.label: Transcript

unitCode.comment: The unit of measurement given using the UN/CEFACT Common Code (3 characters).
unitCode.comment_plain: The unit of measurement given using the UN/CEFACT Common Code (3 characters).

validFrom.comment: The beginning of the validity of offer, price specification, or opening hours data.

validThrough.comment: The end of the validity of offer, price specification, or opening hours data.

value.comment: The value of the product characteristic.
value.comment_plain: The value of the product characteristic.

valueReference.comment: A pointer to a secondary value that provides additional information on the original value, e.g. a reference temperature.
valueReference.comment_plain: A pointer to a secondary value that provides additional information on the original value, e.g. a reference temperature.
valueReference.label: Value Reference

videoFrameSize.comment: The frame size of the video.
videoFrameSize.comment_plain: The frame size of the video.
videoFrameSize.label: Video Frame Size

warranty.comment: The warranty promise(s) included in the offer.
warranty.comment_plain: The warranty promise(s) included in the offer.
warranty.label: Warranty

wordCount.comment: The number of words in the text of the Article.
wordCount.comment_plain: The number of words in the text of the Article.

worstRating.comment: The lowest value allowed in this rating system. If worstRating is omitted, 1 is assumed.
worstRating.comment_plain: The lowest value allowed in this rating system. If worstRating is omitted, 1 is assumed.
worstRating.label: Worst Rating

Brand.comment: A brand is a name used by an organization or business person for labeling a product, product group, or similar.
Brand.comment_plain: A brand is a name used by an organization or business person for labeling a product, product group, or similar.

GeoCoordinates.comment: The geographic coordinates of a place or event.
GeoCoordinates.comment_plain: The geographic coordinates of a place or event.

GeoShape.comment: The geographic shape of a place.
GeoShape.comment_plain: The geographic shape of a place.
GeoShape.label: Geo Shape

Organization.comment: An organization such as a school, NGO, corporation, club, etc.
Organization.comment_plain: An organization such as a school, NGO, corporation, club, etc.
Organization.label: Organization

Person.comment: A person (alive, dead, undead, or fictional).
Person.comment_plain: A person (alive, dead, undead, or fictional).
Person.label: Person

Place.comment: Entities that have a somewhat fixed, physical extension.
Place.comment_plain: Entities that have a somewhat fixed, physical extension.
Place.label: Place

AggregateRating.comment: The average rating based on multiple ratings or reviews.
AggregateRating.comment_plain: The average rating based on multiple ratings or reviews.
AggregateRating.label: Aggregate Rating

Audience.comment: Intended audience for a creative work, i.e. the group for whom the work was created.
Audience.comment_plain: Intended audience for a creative work, i.e. the group for whom the work was created.
Audience.label: Audience

CreativeWork.comment: The most generic kind of creative work, including books, movies, photographs, software programs, etc.
CreativeWork.comment_plain: The most generic kind of creative work, including books, movies, photographs, software programs, etc.
CreativeWork.label: Creative Work

Distance.comment: Properties that take Distances as values are of the form '<Number> <Length unit of measure>'. E.g., '7 ft'
Distance.comment_plain: Properties that take Distances as values are of the form '<Number> <Length unit of measure>'. E.g., '7 ft'
Distance.label: Distance

Event.comment: An event happening at a certain time at a certain location.
Event.comment_plain: An event happening at a certain time at a certain location.
Event.label: Event

MediaObject.comment: An image, video, or audio object embedded in a web page. Note that a creative work may have many media objects associated with it on the same web page. For example, a page about a single song (MusicRecording) may have a music video (VideoObject), and a high and low bandwidth audio stream (2 AudioObject's).
MediaObject.comment_plain: An image, video, or audio object embedded in a web page. Note that a creative work may have many media objects associated with it on the same web page. For example, a page about a single song (MusicRecording) may have a music video (VideoObject), and a high and low bandwidth audio stream (2 AudioObject's).
MediaObject.label: Media Object

Offer.comment: An offer to sell an item—for example, an offer to sell a product, the DVD of a movie, or tickets to an event.
Offer.comment_plain: An offer to sell an item—for example, an offer to sell a product, the DVD of a movie, or tickets to an event.
Offer.label: Offer

OpeningHoursSpecification.comment: A structured value providing information about the opening hours of a place or a certain service inside a place.
OpeningHoursSpecification.comment_plain: A structured value providing information about the opening hours of a place or a certain service inside a place.
OpeningHoursSpecification.label: Opening Hours Specification

QuantitativeValue.comment: A point value or interval for product characteristics and other purposes.
QuantitativeValue.comment_plain: A point value or interval for product characteristics and other purposes.
QuantitativeValue.label: Quantitative Value

Review.comment: A review of an item - for example, a restaurant, movie, or store.
Review.comment_plain: A review of an item - for example, a restaurant, movie, or store.
Review.label: Review

Thing.comment: The most generic type of item.
Thing.comment_plain: The most generic type of item.
Thing.label: Thing

UserComments.comment: The UserInteraction event in which a user comments on an item.
